  %li Next, I installed Anaconda Python:

%pre.round_corner15px
  %code.software
    cd ~
    curl http://repo.continuum.io/archive/Anaconda3-4.0.0-Linux-x86_64.sh > Anaconda3-4.0.0-Linux-x86_64.sh
